<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98600861078477></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98600861078477><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=98600861078477>RE: Equiping my mage</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=98600861078477#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=6400><span id=Scholar>ZomorSoulsaver</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>100 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Mar 30th 10:16 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.22]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I recently did this with my Mage who had hit 20. I went to South karana(the Karana with Splitpaw next to it) and near one of the corners is a hut with a door that does not open. Summon your water pet, go up to the side of the hut when 100% mana and health, and say "Kill you" about 3 times. A hermit(ranger) will rush out, he hits kinda hard for level 20-22, but has low hps. All you need to do is nuke about 2-3 times depending on level to do half damage, and then heal pet accordingly. This guy gives AWESOME exp for 20-25. He also drops a Fine Steel 2Hander about 75% of the time. The best part is HE IS ON A 3MINUTE SPAWN TIME!!!!!!!!!!! of course, this means you will have to use your Water or Air pet because the earth pet will not be able to regen enough health in 3 mins to go again.<br> After he pops again, target your pet, and type /assist. You will get a target on him, so just nuke with your Shock of _____ spell to get him out, and send pet in. Wait for a bit, Nuke, Nuke, Heal pet, Watch the exp flow. Give 1 Fine steeler to your pet so he hits for 24 each time. FS2Handers go for about 5pp to merchants, so that is about 75pp per hour, even more if you can get a newbie to buy it off you for about 10pp. Thats pretty good for about 4 hours per level=about 300pp per level at level 20!!!!!!!!!!!!!! THAT IS SIMPLY AMAZING. So after 5 levels, i have about 2k from one camp, im level 25, and i finally bought myself that damn Stein of Moggok.Talk about being Happy-you can too!<br><br><br>Zomor Soulsaver-Paladin of the 45th circle and a successful Champion of Brell.<br><br>Gnobole Mindshreader-Magician of the 25th season<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
